cpp-kana
------------------------------------------
cpp-kana is a lightweight library for converting Japanese kana to romaji and
vice versa.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libcpp-kana-devel-1.0.2-1bl1
  libcpp-kana1-1.0.2-1bl1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/wolfgitpr/cpp-kana

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/wolfgitpr/cpp-kana/archive/refs/tags/1.0.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack cpp-kana-1.0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./cpp-kana-1.0.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/cpp-kana-1.0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/cpp-kana-1.0.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcpp-kana1-1.0.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcpp-kana-devel-1.0.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(cpp-kana)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/cpp-kana.README
  /usr/share/doc/cpp-kana/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/cpp-kana/README.md

(libcpp-kana1)
  /usr/bin/cygcpp-kana-1.dll

(libcpp-kana-devel)
  /usr/include/cpp-kana/Kana.h
  /usr/include/cpp-kana/KanaGlobal.h
  /usr/include/cpp-kana/KanaRes.h
  /usr/include/cpp-kana/RomajiRes.h
  /usr/include/cpp-kana/U16Str.h
  /usr/lib/cmake/cpp-kana/cpp-kanaConfig.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/cpp-kana/cpp-kanaConfigVersion.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/cpp-kana/cpp-kanaTargets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/cpp-kana/cpp-kanaTargets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libcpp-kana.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/cpp-kana.pc

